{"tid":1879273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"良田村病人 妻母無隔離","createTime":"2020-02-14T06:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T06:15:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0219a3da6b1a4cb4eea020c46b7f5d365e8c9186","tid":1879273,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200214/SMNMSBOP4HIMHQHLFOHAVJPMNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200214%2FSMNMSBOP4HIMHQHLFOHAVJPMNA%2F&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=b82a4468\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200214%2FSMNMSBOP4HIMHQHLFOHAVJPMNA%2F&h=a9dcfffd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200214/SMNMSBOP4HIMHQHLFOHAVJPMNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n良田村病人 妻母無隔離<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200214/large/1581612668_ec56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200214%2Flarge%2F1581612668_ec56.jpg&h=d36e3169&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門良田村染疫老翁的同住女親屬未獲安排入住隔離營。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】再有武漢肺炎患者的密切接觸者疑因隔離營不足而未被安排入住。2月11日確診的屯門良田村66歲老翁，與母親及妻子等同住，屯門新墟區議員張可森引述多名街坊指，與該男患者同住的女親屬未有入住隔離營。前日衞生署派員到患者住所消毒，街坊指因同住親屬未有離開，署方人員不能入屋，只能消毒屋外地方。衞生防護中心昨證實曾與男患者一同用膳的親屬確診感染，令街坊擔心與患者同住的親屬未入隔離營，增加社區傳播病毒風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衞生署稱宿位不足<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：康美樓確診男任職天祥公證行<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心資料顯示，66歲男患者潛伏期內無外遊，同住的妻子和母親沒出現病徵。中心表示，該男患者有11名密切接觸者，兩人分別在屯門醫院及仁濟醫院隔離治療，九人正接受檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n張可森向衞生署查詢，獲回覆指因隔離營爆滿，尤其是日前青衣長康邨康美樓大批市民要入住隔離營，導致宿位不足，正安排66歲男患者的同住女親屬入隔離營。張可森表示，經了解，該兩名同住女親屬沒有離開住所，由其他親友送飯及物資到門口，促政府對有關家庭提供更多支援。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳沛冰"},{"pid":"4e0fa61a603b4be3a6dbf21ba5eb8a1d1263612f","tid":1879273,"uid":151365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:09:05.000Z","msg":"集氣何妖中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8166de56b94dbefde8dfd274c0f71e2eda7bad","tid":1879273,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e407cce7ed77a10b44adc2b0429bbbfd427a7e","tid":1879273,"uid":121985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"係咪何妖條村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9656082d9a5f6d5071d184d0293ecaf8990132a1","tid":1879273,"uid":126153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:15:19.000Z","msg":"關人妻咩事"}]}